## 🛡️ Recommendations

 Enforce strong password policies**
 Implement fail2ban / rate limiting** for SSH
 Disable password authentication → enforce **SSH key-based login**
 Restrict SSH access via firewall (allowlisted IPs only)
 Monitor authentication logs for anomaly spikes

